{"word":"G330 - ἀναθάλλω - anathállō - an-ath-al'-lo - Flourish again","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναθάλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anathállō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ath-al'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Flourish again</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மனம் மலர்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to shoot up, sprout again, grow green again, flourish again"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <b>&#x03B8;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9;</b> <b>thallo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>flourish</i>); to <i>revive:</i> - flourish again.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}